#: src/Admin/SettingsPage.php:2803
msgid "Choose which leaderboard owns the public community ranking. Gamification aggregates every points source - forum reputation, tutorials, media, and activity - into one board. Defer to Jetonomy only if you want its forum reputation board to be the single ranking when Jetonomy is active."
